==Qualification==
Automatic qualifications were granted to the host country and the first four places at the [[Basketball at the 1968 Summer Olympics|previous tournament]]. Additional spots were decided by various continental championships held by [[International Basketball Federation|FIBA]] plus an additional intercontinental championship that granted two extra berths. 

